Sort Characters in a String | Sort the characters of a string in ascending order. |

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "hello";
        char[] ch = str.toCharArray();      //Convert string to character array
        Arrays.sort(ch);                    //Sort the character array
        String s = new String(ch);          //Convert back to string
        System.out.println(s);
    }
}

output:
ehllo
